## 🎯 Sample Use Cases

### 1. Land Cover Classification

```python
from scripts.use_cases import LandCoverClassification

use_case = LandCoverClassification()
results = use_case.run(
    input_raster="data/sentinel2.tif",
    output_path="outputs/land_cover.tif",
    model_path="models/land_cover.h5"
)
print(f"Classification accuracy: {results['statistics']}")
```

### 2. Building Footprint Extraction

```python
from scripts.use_cases import BuildingFootprintExtraction

use_case = BuildingFootprintExtraction()
results = use_case.run(
    input_image="data/aerial.tif",
    output_path="outputs/buildings.geojson",
    min_area=20.0,
    confidence_threshold=0.7
)
print(f"Buildings detected: {results['buildings_detected']}")
```

### 3. Change Detection

```python
from scripts.use_cases import ChangeDetectionAnalysis

use_case = ChangeDetectionAnalysis()
results = use_case.run(
    image_before="data/before.tif",
    image_after="data/after.tif",
    output_path="outputs/change_mask.tif",
    method="siamese_network"
)
print(f"Change percentage: {results['change_percentage']:.2f}%")
```

### 4. Spatial Pattern Analysis

```python
from scripts.use_cases import SpatialPatternAnalysis

use_case = SpatialPatternAnalysis()
results = use_case.run(
    input_data="data/pois.shp",
    output_path="outputs/clusters.geojson",
    algorithm="dbscan"
)
print(f"Clusters found: {results['n_clusters']}")
```

